00:55:06.000 --> 00:55:13.000
And then a new sound gradually droomed into our ears.

756
00:55:13.000 --> 00:55:17.000
A deep sound and all encompassing with no notes in it.

757
00:55:17.000 --> 00:55:22.000
Just a gigantic faraway surge of doom like sound.

758
00:55:22.000 --> 00:55:25.000
It was the heavies.

