00:55:25.000 --> 00:55:32.000
And so now we're talking about the heavy bombers that are going to bring the thunder and there's so many of them

760
00:55:32.000 --> 00:55:42.000
and they're so loud it just drones out every other sound until just this massive faraway surge of a doom like sound.

761
00:55:42.000 --> 00:55:47.000
It was the heavies. They came from directly behind us.

762
00:55:47.000 --> 00:55:51.000
At first they were the mirris dots in the sky.

